value.0: This is a settlement guard insignia for the guard templates.
Another creation of the Axis Nation, this item appears to have many magical symbols upon a finely made robe, you can only guess that it increases some sort of mind power.

A specialized creation of the Third High General of Axis, and the head leader of the Technology developement of Axis.  This helmet was designed to be melted into a crown versain for the Emperor, as to keep the crainium safe from all distractive bothers that could effect the Emperors spells.  Alas, the melted version lost some of its properties, then was placed on one of the many "outdated" technologies of Axis.
Another creation of the Axis science department, this helmet when worn could prove to aid in speech and vocals, making the wearer sound more clear, charming, and perhaps even persuading.

Proving to improve intelligence when worn, not only does this helmet have the ability, but also has the capabilities of increasing the ability to identify spells cast by enemy casters, or to identify magical items. Though to this day, better versions and more powerful versions of this helmet has been invented in the Axis nation, and the old copies are now sold to the rest of the "under-developed" nations.

Seeming to be as light as silk, though having magical properties.  When worn this belt could prove to help prevent failure in the magi's spell casting abilities. Yet another old technology, the Axis Technology department have since created better versions.

A more simple creation of Axis, these basic boots were created for the lesser magi. This belt gives the wearer some protection against magical spells, and also giving him/her better skills in the arcane realm.

Designed for better looks, better intelligence output and defense, these boots were meant to aid in all three of those aspects. Over the time Axis has developed more specifed versions of these boots, making these ones outdated, now sold to the other nations of Amia.
